<p class="intro"><h2 style="margin-bottom: -20px;">CONTACT INFORMATION</h2>
</p>  
<div style="clear: both"></div>
<div class="row"><div class="col-60 col-sm-30 col-md-30"><div style="margin-bottom: -5px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 50px;"><img alt="Exhibitor PR Contact" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/exhibitor-pr-contact_505x285.jpg" />
<h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">List Your PR Contact Information</h3>
</div>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;">Include your company&rsquo;s PR contact within your CES 2018 directory listing, which is shared with registered CES media.</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;">PR contacts also receive the <em>Exhibitor PR News </em>e-newsletter to stay on top of all PR programs and opportunities, important deadlines, and breaking show news.</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><strong><a href="http://ces18.mapyourshow.com/7_0/search.cfm" target="_blank">Add or update your company&rsquo;s PR contact information.</a>&nbsp;&gt;</strong></p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><em>For log-in assistance, contact Map Your Show at 1-888-527-8823.&nbsp;</em></p>
</div><div class="col-60 col-sm-30 col-md-30"><div style="margin-bottom: -5px; margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px; margin-top: 50px;"><a href="https://ces18.exh.mapyourshow.com/6_0/reports/customreport.cfm?ReportID=631" target="_blank"><img alt="See a list of registered media" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/registered-media_505x285.jpg" /></a>

<h3 style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">See a List of Registered Media</h3>
</div>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><strong>Available Dec. 1, 2018</strong><br />
Pull targeted media lists for your news releases and media event pitches. The lists will be updated daily, and you can filter by product category.&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;">If you are hosting an official news conference at CES, the media list will be emailed to you one month in advance.&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin-left: 20px; margin-right: 20px;"><em>NOTE: Media choose whether to list a phone number or email. If none is listed, CES cannot release that information.</em></p>
</div><div class="clearfix visible-sm-block"></div><div class="clearfix visible-md-block visible-lg-block"></div></div><div style="clear: both;">&nbsp;</div>
